#     CH NOTES TO RUN.txt, message for claude.txt, test_write.txt   (harmless empties)
#
#   _templates/                    (HTML + md templates)
#   _skills/                       (the report skill + customizations)
#   _session_notes/                (session notes documenting methodology decisions)
#   deprec/                        (old chat transcripts with methodology context)
#
#   Prototype-build working folders (methodology evidence):
#     bill_george/                 (DRAFT, extracted TTI, scoring xlsx)
#     isaiah/                      (DRAFT, L1 rollup, flags, question bank)
#     MnM/                         (hiring report DRAFT)
#     20260414.mnm.riggs@gmail.com/  (single-respondent working folder)
#     respondents/                 (loose respondent xlsx pulls — older convention)
# ===================================================================
